          <div className="text-7xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6 tracking-tighter">
            {score} <span className="text-2xl text-gray-300 font-bold">/ {questions.length}</span>
          </div>
          <p className="text-gray-400 font-bold mb-10 text-lg">ϋκρύΠ╛ί╛Ωί╛ΙόμΤΎ╝Βώ╗ηόΥΛϊ╕ΜόΨ╣ώκΝύδχόθξύεΜϋσ│ύ┤░ϋπμόηΡϋΙΘίΠξίηΜύ│╛ώΝψήΑΓ</p>
          <Button onClick={onExit} variant="liquid" className="px-12 py-5">ίδηίΙ░ώοΨώιΒ</Button>
